  "commit_message": "docs(ui): correct Never Append tooltip - conflicts continue the shared sequence (#140)\n\nThe Branch Suffix Mode help (org adminSettings + component settings tooltip,\nand the bundling docs) claimed Never Append resolves version conflicts via\n-0, -1, -2 suffixes. The actual (and long-standing) backend behavior on a\nsibling-branch conflict is to continue the component-wide version sequence\n(0.1.0, 0.1.1 -> next is 0.1.2); the -N suffix is only the terminal fallback\nwhen no new version can be derived",
